{
  "texts": [
    "Following this, Sects.",
    "3 and 4 will examine the role of artificial intelligence in olfactory and gustatory research, respectively, and analyze their impacts in these fields.",
    "Section 5 will offer a detailed analysis of AI models applicable to both olfaction and gustation, highlighting the opportunities that AI presents in these areas.",
    "Additionally, Sect. 6 will explore future directions, particularly the integration of emerging technologies with AI and the potential impact of interdisciplinary collaboration on sensory science.",
    "Finally, Sect. 7 will conclude by summarizing the main findings of this review and providing references for future research."
  ]
}